Subject: [RFC net-next 4/6] ethtool: add interface to read standard MAC stats
Date:   Wed, 14 Apr 2021 13:23:23 -0700
Message-Id: <20210414202325.2225774-5-kuba@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
In-Reply-To: <20210414202325.2225774-1-kuba@kernel.org>
References: <20210414202325.2225774-1-kuba@kernel.org>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <netdev.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: netdev@vger.kernel.org

Most of the MAC statistics are included in
struct rtnl_link_stats64, but some fields
are aggregated. Besides it's good to expose
these clearly hardware stats separately.

Signed-off-by: Jakub Kicinski <kuba@kernel.org>
